name: **Cow Island**
description: Cow Island L865-259 Sheet 44 Almost attached to SE Inishbarra, grazed with donkies, but flat and uninteresting to the casual passerby. Cow was cared for once but has been let go. The pass inside Barra is “The Pass” to the N and “Bóthar na nOileán” or the Island Road to the S.
